{
  "id": "adv_love_2603_04_01",
  "title": "Episode 4 Part 1",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_park-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "仕事のことを考えていました",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01-rio017.m4a",
              "text": "その割に、今朝からずっと\n集中出来ていないようだけど",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 204.2332891187,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01-koh011.m4a",
              "text": "すみません……え？　今朝からずっと？\n莉央さんは朝からずっと\n俺のことを見ていたんですか？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 209.0666224521,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 210.6999964397
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01-rio018.m4a",
              "text": "そ、それは、たまたま\n貴方の姿が目に入っただけよ\n変な勘ぐりはしないでちょうだい",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 218.6332891187,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01-koh012.m4a",
              "text": "（もしかして、相手のことが\n気になって落ち着かないのは\n俺だけじゃなかったのか？）",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 226.5333074293,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "莉央さんのことを考えていました",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_plan-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 232.5666407627
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01-koh016.m4a",
              "text": "今日は朝からずっと\n莉央さんのことばかり考えて\n仕事が手につきませんでした",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 232.5666407627,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01-rio019.m4a",
              "text": "……馬鹿なこと言ってないで\n仕事に集中しなさい",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 237.9999659579,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01-koh014.m4a",
              "text": "（好きだって想いをアピールしてみたけど\n莉央さんの態度は素っ気ないな……）",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 241.8332992912,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01-koh015.m4a",
              "text": "（俺、本当に莉央さんと付き合ってるのかな\nまさか、昨日の出来事は全部、俺の願望が\n見せた妄想だったなんてことは……）",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 247.4999659579,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": null,
              "text": "あの、確認なんですけど\n俺と莉央さんは本当に恋人に……\nあいたっ！　どうしてデコピンするんですか",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 257.4999659579,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_chop-01.m4a",
                  "delay": 4663.360763300034
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01-rio020.m4a",
              "text": "こんなに人が沢山いる所で、急に変なことを\n言おうとするからでしょ。まったく……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 266.5666265209,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "嫌じゃありません！",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_heart-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 406.0666387278
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01-rio032.m4a",
              "text": "そんなにムキになって否定するなんて……\n貴方って素直で可愛いわね",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 406.0666387278,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "嬉しいけど恥ずかしいです……",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_heart-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 413.9666387278
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01-rio033.m4a",
              "text": "もしかして照れてるの？\n照れてる貴方も可愛いわね",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 413.9666387278,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "仕事帰りに呼び出したりして悪かったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.4666666865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、全然大丈夫です\nわざわざ俺を呼び出すってことは\n告白の返事を聞かせてくれるんですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.499999845,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 12.8333336234
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "ええ\n真剣に考えて、ちゃんと答えを出したから\n聞いてもらえるかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.8333336234,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 20.8000002901
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それで、返事なんだけど\n私は、貴方を……あ、貴方の……\n貴方が……あな、あな、あな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.8000002901,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 34.6000002901
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "ふー……ごめんなさい\nこういうことには慣れていなくて\n自分でも驚くほど緊張してるみたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.6000002901,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 43.7333338777
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "慣れていない？　でも、莉央さんくらい\n綺麗な人なら、告白されるのも断るのも\nよくあることじゃないんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.7333338777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "stop",
      "startTime": 51.721043686
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 52.4333338777
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "私が綺麗だなんて\nそんな風に言ってくれるのは\n{user}君だけよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.4333338777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_flashback-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 58.5000005443
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "いつも、怖いだのキツいだの言われて\n告白どころか、恋愛の対象として\n見られたこともなかったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.5000005443,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 66.2999959667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですか？\n莉央さんは恋愛経験豊富で\n大人の恋愛にも詳しいと思っていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.2999959667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "なぜかよく勘違いされるのよね\n私ってそんなに恋愛しているように\n見えるのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.4666626334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 80.4666626334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "同僚からもよく恋愛相談されるし……\nそのたびに見栄を張って、知ったかぶって\n恋愛に詳しいフリをする私も悪いんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.4666626334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、莉央さんの恋愛経験は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.9999913891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_04_01-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "誰かと付き合ったことなんて一度もないわ\nだから……\n{user}君が初めての恋人よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.6666626334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "stop",
      "startTime": 98.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 101.0333318074
    },
